data.description: Seller has an assumable mortgage under 4% - buyer to qualify  * NOTE -  SCPW is repairing a water main at a neighboring property, so there is some construction on the cul de sac.  There have been no problems at 4 Duchess Ct. , it is strictly limited to the neighbor.  SCPW will be cleaning up shortly - sorry for any inconvenience Affordable 3 bedroom, 1 bath, 1052 sqft home in great location with charming curb appeal.  This comfortable home has plenty of natural light and a fenced yard, ready for kids or pets to enjoy.  It's a short walk to the neighborhood pool (membership fee required), park and the Sawmill Branch Trail entrance.  Award winning DD2 schools are close by and there's easy access to shopping, restaurants, downtown Summerville and Charleston.  A lovely place to call home
